window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>As the Stone Raiders come into a time of peace, they set upon building up their guild hall and getting back to raiding.</p> <p>Without the worries of immediate battles and constant quests, Dave and Party Zero are free to pursue their passions. New discoveries will be made and advances taken. They've got big plans and ideas for the future. What they start now will form and shape that future.</p> <p>In this time of change, possibilities will rise, and opportunities will be grasped. It's time to build for the future.</p>"; 
